description: Join DogeWorld - the only collectible collection with a supply of 1001 inscriptions starting under 300k. Featuring 121 unique characters, drawn pixel by pixel and expanded into four rarity tiers. 33 specials complete the puzzle, including a themed collection dedicated to BITCOIN JPGs - of which we are the exclusive partners. But the story doesn't end here. Our mission is to create a vibrant and playful community united by strength and awareness in the crypto space. Let the adventure begin!
name: DogeWorld
